bach_open_taxonomy.SeriesLocationStack.objectiv¶

property SeriesLocationStack.objectiv¶

Accessor for Objectiv stack data. All methods of json can also be accessed with this accessor. Same as obj

class LocationStack(series_object)
property LocationStack.feature_stack

Returns the feature stack from the location stack. The context objects only contain the _type and a id key.

property LocationStack.navigation_features

Returns the navigation stack from the location stack.

property LocationStack.nice_name

Returns a nice name for the location stack. This is a human readable name for the data in the feature stack.
